<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cut-back-on">cut back on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>缩减；削减</strong></h4>
<p>to reduce the amount, size, cost etc. of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Several companies are <strong>cutting back on</strong> staff at the moment. 
目前，有几家公司正在裁员。</p></div></div>